        </para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    <emphasis role="bold">Initial event firing time </emphasis>
                </para>
                <para>
                    One event is generated on the unique output event port if Event time is
                    larger than equal to zero, if not, no event is generated.
                </para>
                <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1</para>
            </listitem>
